<h2>Welcome to my personal project page!</br>
Cronache della sepiolite -Chronicles of sepiolitis-</br>
is a story born out of boredom in 2020,
which I am writing with the help of my partner.</br>
Gradually from a thing born for fun it became bigger and bigger,
and we started to take it with more and more seriousness,
until we started working on its possible graphic novel.
Here you will find a series of artwork 
and character designs of the protagonists of this story</h2>
